OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy
OL,6,Facross the region tonight, with
OL,7,Ffurther outbreaks of light and patchy
OL,8,Frain, particularly across the hills. A
OL,9,Ffew clear spells developing too with
OL,10,Fsome mist and fog patches possible.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FRemaining cloudy on Sunday
OL,13,Fwith outbreaks of light rain and
OL,14,Fdrizzle where the cloud thickens. Some
OL,15,Fbrighter spells possible too. Near
OL,16,Fnormal temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
